              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Sc-45 target was prepared by vacuum evaporation of",
                "natural scandium.",
                "The Ca-44 target was fabricated by vacuum evaporation",
                "of the enriched carbonate, the isotopic compositions",
                "was Ca-44 98.56%, Ca-40 1.35%, Ca-42 0.04%, Ca-43 0.05%",
                "and Ca-46,48 less than 0.01%."
